title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre willing to take charge and step in to resolve a work issue today. However, its advisable to go in with your eyes wide open, since the task likely demands a significant amount of labor or energy to organize others for help. Fortunately, your valiant efforts create the desired results as the hardworking Virgo Moon smoothly trines innovative Uranus in your 10th House of Career. Nevertheless, you can always tap into your creativity to manage any more surprises that pop up. Zig Ziglar wrote, "Expect the best. Prepare for the worst. Capitalize on what comes."
